casebody.data:
Thursday, April 25, 1991

MOTION DOCKET

90-2282. State v. Cummings.

Cuyahoga County, No. 57558. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s motion for stay. Upon consideration thereof, IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective April 24, 1991.

Sweeney, J., dissents.
